"kv2.7:10.3": "Nanu vuttaṃ bhagavatā—",
"kv2.7:10.4": "“seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, makkaṭo araññe pavane caramāno sākhaṃ gaṇhati, taṃ muñcitvā aññaṃ gaṇhati, taṃ muñcitvā aññaṃ gaṇhati;",
